  "name": "RPlog_Fett_vs_Firecats",
  "title": "Fett vs. Firecats",
  "summary": "In a Mos Eisley docking bay, the bounty hunter Boba Fett stakes out the freighter Forge of Hope, having tracked NRI agent Ikihsa Enb'Zik and a substantial bounty on his crew. As the Sullustan returns from a supply run with the Horansi warrior Snarl and the recovering Jedi Brandis, Fett ambushes them, declaring Enb'Zik and his crew enemies of the Empire, wanted dead or alive. The standoff erupts into a firefight: Brandis lands a Force-driven blow to Fett's helmet and is shot through the thigh in retaliation, while Snarl charges as a 550-pound projectile and slams the hunter into a nearby hull, stunning but not breaking him. With the Forge's laser cannons trained on him and Marines pouring down the ramp, Fett produces a grenade to deter a finishing blow. The crew retreats aboard the ship with the wounded Brandis, and as they lift off, the battered but undefeated Fett fires a short-range tracker onto the Forge, vowing to hunt them again.",
